<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Peace Token Project</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts: Playfair Display for a elegant, aesthetic serif, and Montserrat for clean UI -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --heavenly-blue: #a1c4fd;
            --heavenly-pink: #c2e9fb;
            --gold: #dfba6b;
            --text-dark: #2c3e50;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body, html {
            height: 100%;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* Animated Sky/Cloud Background */
        .sky-bg {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--heavenly-blue) 0%, var(--heavenly-pink) 100%);
            z-index: -2;
        }

        .clouds-container {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0.4;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .cloud {
            position: absolute;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 200px;
            filter: blur(20px);
        }

        .cloud1 { width: 400px; height: 120px; top: 15%; left: -20%; animation: floatClouds 55s linear infinite; }
        .cloud2 { width: 600px; height: 180px; top: 45%; left: -35%; animation: floatClouds 85s linear infinite; animation-delay: -20s; }
        .cloud3 { width: 350px; height: 100px; top: 70%; left: -15%; animation: floatClouds 40s linear infinite; animation-delay: -10s; }

        @keyframes floatClouds {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
            100% { transform: translateX(250vw); }
        }

        /* Sexy, elegant typography */
        h1, h2, h3, .sexy-font {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* App Layout */
        .wrapper {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Audio Control Pill */
        .audio-pill {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
        }
        .audio-pill:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Token Display Box */
        .token-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 40px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        /* The Coin Graphic */
        .coin-graphic {
            width: 160px;
            height: 160px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #f3e7e9 100%);
            border: 4px solid var(--gold);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(223, 186, 107, 0.3);
            font-size: 3rem;
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.6s ease;
        }
        .coin-graphic::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 5px; left: 5px; right: 5px; bottom: 5px;
            border: 1px dashed var(--gold);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .spin {
            animation: spinCoin 0.8s ease-in-out;
        }
        @keyframes spinCoin {
            0% { transform: rotateY(0deg) scale(1); }
            50% { transform: rotateY(180deg) scale(1.1); }
            100% { transform: rotateY(360deg) scale(1); }
        }

        .message-text {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #34495e;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            min-height: 80px;
        }

        /* Action Buttons */
        .btn {
            background: var(--text-dark);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 16px 36px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            background: #1a252f;
        }

        /* Support & Help Sections */
        .support-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .support-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        .support-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 25px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        .support-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        .support-card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            opacity: 0.85;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .support-link {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Footers & Legal Disclaimers */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            padding-top: 30px;
        }

        .disclaimer-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: justify;
            opacity: 0.8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Smooth Heavenly Layers -->
    <div class="sky-bg"></div>
    <div class="clouds-container">
        <div class="cloud cloud1"></div>
        <div class="cloud cloud2"></div>
        <div class="cloud cloud3"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hidden audio elements utilizing copyright-free atmospheric sounds -->
    <audio id="peacefulMusic" loop src="https://mixkit.co"></audio>

    <div class="wrapper">
        <!-- Interactive Music Control -->
        <div class="audio-pill" onclick="toggleMusic()">
            <span id="musicIcon">🎵</span> <span id="musicText">Enable Peaceful Music</span>
        </div>

        <header>
            <h1>The Peace Token</h1>
            <p>A gentle breath of digital comfort for your soul.</p>
        </header>

        <!-- Main Novelty Engine Box -->
        <main class="token-box">
            <div id="coin" class="coin-graphic">🕊️</div>
            
            <div id="messageDisplay" class="message-text">
                "Welcome, beautiful soul. Press the button below to draw your token of comfort."
            </div>

            <!-- This mirrors where real global payments via Stripe Checkout / PayPal SDK integrate -->
            <button class="btn" onclick="drawToken()">Receive a Peace Token ($1.00 USD)</button>
        </main>

        <!-- Global Crisis Support Resources for Troubled/Desperate People -->
        <section class="support-grid">
            <div class="support-card">
                <h3>For Desperate or Troubled Hearts</h3>
                <p>If you are feeling completely alone, overwhelmed, or in deep distress, please reach out to professional hands waiting to help you across the globe right now.</p>
                <a href="https://findahelpline.com" target="_blank" class="support-link">Find a Free, Confidential Local Helpline</a>
            </div>

            <div class="support-card">
                <h3>Help for the Needy & Alone</h3>
                <p>No matter where you live worldwide, community networks stand ready to offer tangible aid, meal programs, and shelter if you are struggling to get by.</p>
